scenes.description: Koseki Bijou describes her first date scenario involving a movie and seeking comfort.
The group reacts to Bijou's scenario and prepares for the next person.
Fuwawa Abyssgard presents her first date scenario, focusing on spending quality time alone.
Fuwawa continues her scenario, which is presented as 'How Nerissa hears it'.
Nerissa reacts to Fuwawa and invites the next 'bachelor' to the stage.
Shiori Novella presents a humorous first date scenario involving money and roses.
Nerissa concludes the first round and moves on to the next question.
Nerissa introduces the second topic, 'First Date Surprise', and puts on her blindfold.
Fuwawa starts her surprise scenario with a night walk by the water.
